  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Operations Manager / Facilities Manager (Soft Services - Cleaning)",
  "description": "<p>We are hiring an Operations Manager to lead our soft services division. This role requires immediate, demonstrated competence in three non-negotiable areas. If you lack these capabilities, do not apply.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Non-Negotiable Requirements</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>1. Financial &amp; Administrative Autonomy (Advanced Excel):</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Required:</strong>      Microsoft Advanced Excel Certification or equivalent proven capability.</li>\n  <li><strong>Must:</strong>              Independently manage site budgets, cost analysis, and produce all required internal financial reports. Your system competence must support full autonomy over site performance data.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>2. Client Management &amp; Commercial Safeguarding:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Required:</strong>    Documented track record in effective Client Relationship Management       (CRM).</li>\n  <li><strong>Must:</strong>            Produce and present all necessary client-facing and billing reports to ensure <strong>zero obstruction to monthly invoicing</strong>. You must possess deep contractual knowledge to actively protect against scope creep.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>3. End-to-End Local Recruitment Solutions:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Required:</strong>    Direct ownership of the entire recruitment cycle for <strong>Singapore Citizens/PRs</strong>—from candidate search and sourcing to successful employment on-site.</li>\n  <li><strong>Must:</strong>            Solve all local manpower challenges and reliably ensure full, high-quality staffing for all sites.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Drive operational excellence and ensure high service standards across all soft services contracts.</li>\n  <li>Lead, mentor, and manage supervisors and frontline staff.</li>\n  <li>Implement efficiency improvements and cost-optimization initiatives.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>To Apply:</strong> Submit your CV, focusing on specific evidence of meeting the three non-negotiable requirements listed above.</p>",
